seo: ApacheStruts2,CVE-2018-11776,远程代码执行漏洞,检测,插件
summary: 该插件用于检测目标系统是否存在ApacheStruts2(s2-057)_CVE-2018-11776远程代码执行漏洞，通过发送特定payload判断漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the target system has the ApacheStruts2(s2-057)_CVE-2018-11776 Remote Code Execution vulnerability by sending a specific payload to determine if the vulnerability exists.
